bEMcgo","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec0jtP2jmhWEog8i","target":"recgAScrne6IJlIRY","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec0jtP2jmhWEog8i","target":"recuBx2LEnNR6q2X3","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec0jtP2jmhWEog8i","target":"recsX4et9ux7g07Zg","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec0jtP2jmhWEog8i","target":"recM9XRLGW2MiGPpZ","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec0jtP2jmhWEog8i","target":"recHQ6dZlDsEgw45z","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec0jtP2jmhWEog8i","target":"recpqKANUDcRgN4HU","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec0jtP2jmhWEog8i","target":"recJdr0KdZkuEwio5","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec0jtP2jmhWEog8i","target":"rec9FmVbRkqnkXn8n","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec0jtP2jmhWEog8i","target":"recmCYBlOy0l5D1eB","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec0jtP2jmhWEog8i","target":"recrydf4wCTnlOHEO","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec0jtP2jmhWEog8i","target":"recQ1bj3p4Lj5MYY6","label":"event"}],"verses":[{"id":"rec0L6HmCaKKRtrUO","ref":"Isa.21.1","text":"The burden of the desert of the sea. As whirlwinds in the south pass through; so it cometh from the desert, from a terrible land.","year":-714},{"id":"rec1LZeLvwBPfZbjl","ref":"Isa.21.2","text":"A grievous vision is declared unto me; the treacherous dealer dealeth treacherously, and the spoiler spoileth. Go up, O Elam: besiege, O Media; all the sighing thereof have I made to cease.","year":-714},{"id":"recMxAFCPp2yaAhaB","ref":"Isa.21.3","text":"Therefore are my loins filled with pain: pangs have taken hold upon me, as the pangs of a woman that travaileth: I was bowed down at the hearing of it; I was dismayed at the seeing of it.","year":-714},{"id":"recHEbrpjudMAyiuV","ref":"Isa.21.4","text":"My heart panted, fearfulness affrighted me: the night of my pleasure hath he turned into fear unto me.","year":-714},{"id":"recVY14BNiDWmtWHr","ref":"Isa.21.5","text":"Prepare the table, watch in the watchtower, eat, drink: arise, ye princes, and anoint the shield.","year":-714},{"id":"recP4cNv4tvRWlgd5","ref":"Isa.21.6","text":"For thus hath the Lord said unto me, Go, set a watchman, let him declare what he seeth.","year":-714},{"id":"recfA0z4mu7sGnbCz","ref":"Isa.21.7","text":"And he saw a chariot with a couple of horsemen, a chariot of asses, and a chariot of camels; and he hearkened diligently with much heed:","year":-714},{"id":"recOnaolaeHWBipAz","ref":"Isa.21.8","text":"And he cried, A lion: My lord, I stand continually upon the watchtower in the daytime, and I am set in my ward whole nights:","year":-714}]}
